      "content": "it's hard to argue with that. \"merciful release\" is exactly how it feels. like, if the world is going to end anyway, why stay for the worst parts of it? it's like everyone is telling me to keep breathing just to suffer more, but it doesn't feel like strength, it just feels... unnecessary. like i'm just prolonging the pain for no reason. doesn't it seem more logical to just opt out before the real chaos starts?",
